  [3]: https://developer.android.com/reference/android/app/Activity#onActivityResult(int,%20int,%20android.content.Intent)
  [4]: https://developer.android.com/reference/androidx/recyclerview/widget/RecyclerView.ViewHolder#getAbsoluteAdapterPosition()

